Gondhal (Drama) and Bhajans, Kolhapur, India, January 1st, 1983

[Shri Mataji speaks at 48:08]They are playing the praise of the Goddesses, also my praise and they are thankful to you for really [inaudible] them in a simple expression of your love for your Mother.

And it’s a very simple drama for village that they perform, entertain people in that they talk of God and all the work of the Goddess. It’s a very good way to learn- to entertain the villagers and to tell them about the Goddess [inaudible] for this, they have this play. And [inaudible] very well.

